日本語版

> ブラウザの起動に失敗しました。
> ＜次のアクション＞

英語版

> The browser failed to launch.
> \<Next Action>
>  \* If a screen for selecting a user, such as "Who's using Chrome?", is displayed on startup, you need to specify which profile to use.
> ・First, try entering "Default" in the "Profile Name" option to see if this resolves the issue.
> ・If that does not work, you'll need to provide the profile's folder name. Note that the display name in the browser can be different from the actual folder name. Please open your "User Data Directory", locate the folder you want to use (e.g., "Profile 1"), and enter its name exactly as it appears into the "Profile Name" field.
